{
  "stem": "7414.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I come from Przemysl, from a very backward country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know what is Vogue, I didn't know what was patterns, I did not know what it is.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I told her no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I told her I haven't got work-- she told me everything will be taken care of.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was my first big mistake which I made, because I didn't know what it is and I told her no.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I wanted to learn, try it, really saw that I can support myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I finished the school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I found a place with a Polish dressmaker, a good dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I learned there practical thing, and I then when she left, all her customers stayed with me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was working privately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The high class was one of a kind, you know, for those Jewish woman from Poland who had those ideas that they have to have the best.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they had enough money then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was working like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Meantime my husband established himself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The same thing, you see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he started to earn well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I stopped to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got very sick in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I stopped work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I kept only two or three good and pleasant customers, with whom I went very friendly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just not to forget what I-- and I had nothing to do the whole day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By now, Michael was in school, you know, and we bought a flat in Paris.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we loved every minute of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Money or not money, hunger or not hunger at the beginning, but we really loved it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then in '52, before '52 when it was the Korean War, and the panic settled all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
